3-L104"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/FieldOpFreeAlgebra/Basic.html#FieldSpecification.FieldOpFreeAlgebra.ofFieldOpListF\"><span class=\"name\">FieldSpecification</span>.<span class=\"name\">FieldOpFreeAlgebra</span>.<span class=\"name\">ofFieldOpListF</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">𝓕</span> : <a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/FieldSpecification/Basic.html#FieldSpecification\">FieldSpecification</a>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">φs</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">𝓕</span>.<a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/FieldSpecification/Basic.html#FieldSpecification.FieldOp\">FieldOp</a></span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">𝓕</span>.<a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/FieldOpFreeAlgebra/Basic.html#FieldSpecification.FieldOpFreeAlgebra\">FieldOpFreeAlgebra</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"For a field specification `𝓕`, and a list `φs` of `𝓕.FieldOp`,\n`𝓕.ofFieldOpListF φs` is defined as the element of `𝓕.FieldOpFreeAlgebra`\nobtained by the product of `ofFieldOpF φ` for each `φ` in `φs`.\nFor example `ofFieldOpListF [φ₁, φ₂, φ₃] = ofFieldOpF φ₁ * ofFieldOpF φ₂ * ofFieldOpF φ₃`. ","docLink":"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/FieldOpFreeAlgebra/Basic.html#FieldSpecification.FieldOpFreeAlgebra.ofFieldOpListF","kind":"def","line":97,"name":"FieldSpecification.FieldOpFreeAlgebra.ofFieldOpListF","sourceLink":"https://github.com/HEPLean/PhysLean#L97-L101"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/FieldOpFreeAlgebra/Basic.html#FieldSpecification.FieldOpFreeAlgebra.ofFieldOpF\"><span class=\"name\">FieldSpecification</span>.<span class=\"name\">FieldOpFreeAlgebra</span>.<span class=\"name\">ofFieldOpF</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">𝓕</span> : <a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/FieldSpecification/Basic.html#FieldSpecification\">FieldSpecification</a>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">φ</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">𝓕</span>.<a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/FieldSpecification/Basic.html#FieldSpecification.FieldOp\">FieldOp</a></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">𝓕</span>.<a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/FieldOpFreeAlgebra/Basic.html#FieldSpecification.FieldOpFreeAlgebra\">FieldOpFreeAlgebra</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"For a field specification `𝓕`, and an element `φ` of `𝓕.FieldOp`,\n`ofFieldOpF φ` is the element of `𝓕.FieldOpFreeAlgebra` formed by summing over\n`ofCrAnOpF` of the\ncreation and annihilation parts of `φ`.\n\nFor example, for `φ` an incoming asymptotic field operator we get\n`ofCrAnOpF ⟨φ, ()⟩`, and for `φ` a\nposition field operator we get `ofCrAnOpF ⟨φ, .create⟩ + ofCrAnOpF ⟨φ, .annihilate⟩`. ","docLink":"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/FieldOpFreeAlgebra/Basic.html#FieldSpecification.FieldOpFreeAlgebra.ofFieldOpF","kind":"def","line":86,"name":"FieldSpecification.FieldOpFreeAlgebra.ofFieldOpF","sourceLink":"https://github.com/HEPLean/PhysLean#L86-L95"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">theorem</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/FieldOpFreeAlgebra/Basic.html#FieldSpecification.FieldOpFreeAlgebra.ofCrAnListF_singleton\"><span class=\"name\">FieldSpecification</span>.<span class=\"name\">FieldOpFreeAlgebra</span>.<span class=\"name\">ofCrAnListF_singleton</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">𝓕</span> : <a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/FieldSpecification/Basic.html#FieldSpecification\">FieldSpecification</a>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">φ</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">𝓕</span>.<a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/FieldSpecification/CrAnFieldOp.html#FieldSpecification.CrAnFieldOp\">CrAnFieldOp</a></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/FieldOpFreeAlgebra/Basic.html#FieldSpecification.FieldOpFreeAlgebra.ofCrAnListF\">ofCrAnListF</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List.cons\">[</a><span class=\"fn\">φ</span><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List.cons\">]</a></span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Eq\">=</a> <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/FieldOpFreeAlgebra/Basic.html#FieldSpecification.FieldOpFreeAlgebra.ofCrAnOpF\">ofCrAnOpF</a> <span class=\"fn\">φ</span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/FieldOpFreeAlgebra/Basic.html#FieldSpecification.FieldOpFreeAlgebra.ofCrAnListF_singleton","kind":"theorem","line":83,"name":"FieldSpecification.FieldOpFreeAlgebra.ofCrAnListF_singleton","sourceLink":"https://github.com/HEPLean/PhysLean#L83-L84"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">theorem</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/FieldOpFreeAlgebra/Basic.html#FieldSpecification.FieldOpFreeAlgebra.ofCrAnListF_append\"><span class=\"name\">FieldSpecification</span>.<span class=\"name\">FieldOpFreeAlgebra</span>.<span class=\"name\">ofCrAnListF_append</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">𝓕</span> : <a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/FieldSpecification/Basic.html#FieldSpecification\">FieldSpecification</a>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">φs </span><span class=\"fn\">φs'</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">𝓕</span>.<a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/FieldSpecification/CrAnFieldOp.html#FieldSpecification.CrAnFieldOp\">CrAnFieldOp</a></span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/FieldOpFreeAlgebra/Basic.html#FieldSpecification.FieldOpFreeAlgebra.ofCrAnListF\">ofCrAnListF</a> (<span class=\"fn\">φs</span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#HAppend.hAppend\">++</a> <span class=\"fn\">φs'</span>)</span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Eq\">=</a> <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/FieldOpFreeAlgebra/Basic.html#FieldSpecification.FieldOpFreeAlgebra.ofCrAnListF\">ofCrAnListF</a> <span class=\"fn\">φs</span></span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#HMul.hMul\">*</a> <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/FieldOpFreeAlgebra/Basic.html#FieldSpecification.FieldOpFreeAlgebra.ofCrAnListF\">ofCrAnListF</a> <span class=\"fn\">φs'</span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/FieldOpFreeAlgebra/Basic.html#FieldSpecification.FieldOpFreeAlgebra.ofCrAnListF_append","kind":"theorem","line":79,"name":"FieldSpecification.FieldOpFreeAlgebra.ofCrAnListF_append","sourceLink":"https://github.com/HEPLean/PhysLean#L79-L81"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">theorem</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/FieldOpFreeAlgebra/Basic.html#FieldSpecification.FieldOpFreeAlgebra.ofCrAnListF_cons\"><span class=\"name\">F