"name":"FieldSpecification.FieldOpFreeAlgebra.ofCrAnListF_cons","sourceLink":"https://github.com/HEPLean/PhysLean#L76-L77"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">theorem</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/FieldOpFreeAlgebra/Basic.html#FieldSpecification.FieldOpFreeAlgebra.ofCrAnListF_nil\"><span class=\"name\">FieldSpecification</span>.<span class=\"name\">FieldOpFreeAlgebra</span>.<span class=\"name\">ofCrAnListF_nil</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">𝓕</span> : <a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/FieldSpecification/Basic.html#FieldSpecification\">FieldSpecification</a>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/FieldOpFreeAlgebra/Basic.html#FieldSpecification.FieldOpFreeAlgebra.ofCrAnListF\">ofCrAnListF</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List.nil\">[</a><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List.nil\">]</a></span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Eq\">=</a> <span class=\"fn\">1</span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/FieldOpFreeAlgebra/Basic.html#FieldSpecification.FieldOpFreeAlgebra.ofCrAnListF_nil","kind":"theorem","line":73,"name":"FieldSpecification.FieldOpFreeAlgebra.ofCrAnListF_nil","sourceLink":"https://github.com/HEPLean/PhysLean#L73-L74"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/FieldOpFreeAlgebra/Basic.html#FieldSpecification.FieldOpFreeAlgebra.ofCrAnListF\"><span class=\"name\">FieldSpecification</span>.<span class=\"name\">FieldOpFreeAlgebra</span>.<span class=\"name\">ofCrAnListF</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">𝓕</span> : <a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/FieldSpecification/Basic.html#FieldSpecification\">FieldSpecification</a>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">φs</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">𝓕</span>.<a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/FieldSpecification/CrAnFieldOp.html#FieldSpecification.CrAnFieldOp\">CrAnFieldOp</a></span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">𝓕</span>.<a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/FieldOpFreeAlgebra/Basic.html#FieldSpecification.FieldOpFreeAlgebra\">FieldOpFreeAlgebra</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"For a field specification `𝓕`, and a list `φs` of `𝓕.CrAnFieldOp`,\n`ofCrAnListF φs` is defined as the element of `𝓕.FieldOpFreeAlgebra`\nobtained by the product of `ofCrAnListF φ` for each `φ` in `φs`.\nFor example `ofCrAnListF [φ₁, φ₂, φ₃] = ofCrAnOpF φ₁ * ofCrAnOpF φ₂ * ofCrAnOpF φ₃`.\nThe set of all `ofCrAnListF φs` forms a basis of `FieldOpFreeAlgebra 𝓕`. ","docLink":"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/FieldOpFreeAlgebra/Basic.html#FieldSpecification.FieldOpFreeAlgebra.ofCrAnListF","kind":"def","line":66,"name":"FieldSpecification.FieldOpFreeAlgebra.ofCrAnListF","sourceLink":"https://github.com/HEPLean/PhysLean#L66-L71"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">theorem</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/FieldOpFreeAlgebra/Basic.html#FieldSpecification.FieldOpFreeAlgebra.universality\"><span class=\"name\">FieldSpecification</span>.<span class=\"name\">FieldOpFreeAlgebra</span>.<span class=\"name\">universality</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">𝓕</span> : <a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/FieldSpecification/Basic.html#FieldSpecification\">FieldSpecification</a>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">A</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Algebra/Ring/Defs.html#Semiring\">Semiring</a> <span class=\"fn\">A</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Algebra/Algebra/Defs.html#Algebra\">Algebra</a> <a href=\"./Mathlib/Data/Complex/Basic.html#Complex\">ℂ</a> <span class=\"fn\">A</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">f</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">𝓕</span>.<a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/FieldSpecification/CrAnFieldOp.html#FieldSpecification.CrAnFieldOp\">CrAnFieldOp</a></span> → <span class=\"fn\">A</span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Logic/ExistsUnique.html#ExistsUnique\">∃!</a> <span class=\"fn\">g</span> <a href=\"./Mathlib/Logic/ExistsUnique.html#ExistsUnique\">:</a> <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">𝓕</span>.<a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/FieldOpFreeAlgebra/Basic.html#FieldSpecification.FieldOpFreeAlgebra\">FieldOpFreeAlgebra</a></span> <a href=\"./Mathlib/Algebra/Algebra/Hom.html#AlgHom\">→ₐ[</a><a href=\"./Mathlib/Data/Complex/Basic.html#Complex\">ℂ</a><a href=\"./Mathlib/Algebra/Algebra/Hom.html#AlgHom\">]</a> <span class=\"fn\">A</span><a href=\"./Mathlib/Logic/ExistsUnique.html#ExistsUnique\">,</a> <span class=\"fn\">⇑<span class=\"fn\">g</span></span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Function.comp\">∘</a> <a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/FieldOpFreeAlgebra/Basic.html#FieldSpecification.FieldOpFreeAlgebra.ofCrAnOpF\">ofCrAnOpF</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Eq\">=</a> <span class=\"fn\">f</span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"The algebra `𝓕.FieldOpFreeAlgebra` satisfies the universal property that for any other algebra\n`A` (e.g. the operator algebra of the theory) with a map `f : 𝓕.CrAnFieldOp → A` (e.g.\nthe inclusion of the creation and annihilation parts of field operators into the\noperator algebra) there is a unique algebra map `g : 𝓕.FieldOpFreeAlgebra → A`\nsuch that `g ∘ ofCrAnOpF = f`.\n\nThe unique `g` is given by `FreeAlgebra.lift ℂ f`.\n","docLink":"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/FieldOpFreeAlgebra/Basic.html#FieldSpecification.FieldOpFreeAlgebra.universality","kind":"theorem","line":47,"name":"FieldSpecification.FieldOpFreeAlgebra.universality","sourceLink":"https://github.com/HEPLean/PhysLean#L47-L64"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/FieldOpFreeAlgebra/Basic.html#FieldSpecification.FieldOpFreeAlgebra.ofCrAnOpF\"><span class=\"name\">FieldSpecification</span>.<span class=\"name\">FieldOpFreeAlgebra</span>.<span class=\"name\">ofCrAnOpF</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">𝓕</span> : <a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/FieldSpecification/Basic.html#FieldSpecification\">FieldSpecification</a>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">φ</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">𝓕</span>.<a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/FieldSpecification/CrAnFieldOp.html#FieldSpecification.CrAnFieldOp\">CrAnFieldOp</a></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">𝓕</span>.<a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/FieldOpFreeAlgebra/Basic.html#FieldSpecification.FieldOpFreeAlgebra\">FieldOpFreeAlgebra</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"For a field specification `𝓕`, and a element `φ` of `𝓕.CrAnFieldOp`,\n`ofCrAnOpF φ` is defined as the element of `𝓕.FieldOpFreeAlgebra` formed by `φ`. ","docLink":"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/FieldOpFreeAlgebra/Basic.html#FieldSpecification.FieldOpFreeAlgebra.ofCrAnOpF","kind":"def","line":42,"name":"FieldSpecification.FieldOpFreeAlgebra.ofCrAnOpF","sourceLink":"https://github.com/HEPLean/PhysLean#L42-L45"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">abbrev</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/FieldOpFreeAlgebra/Basic.html#FieldSpecification.FieldOpFreeAlgebra\"><span class=\"name\">FieldSpecification</span>.<span class=\"name\">FieldOpFreeAlgebra</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">𝓕</span> : <a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/FieldSpecification/Basic.html#FieldSpecification\">FieldSpecification</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"For a field specification `𝓕`, the algebra `𝓕.FieldOpFreeAlgebra` is\nthe free algebra generated by `𝓕.CrAnFieldOp`. ","docLink":"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/FieldOpFreeAlgebra/Basic.html#FieldSpecification.FieldOpFreeAlgebra","kind":"def","line":36,"name":"FieldSpecification.FieldOpFreeAlgebra","sourceLink":"https://github.com/HEPLean/PhysLean#L36-L38"}}],"imports":["Init","PhysLean.QFT.PerturbationTheory.FieldSpecification.CrAnSection"],"instances":[{"className":"Coe","name":"FieldSpecification.FieldOpFreeAlgebra.instCoeListFieldOp","typeNames":["List","FieldSpecification.FieldOpFreeAlgebra"]}],"name":"PhysLean.QFT.PerturbationTheory.FieldOpFreeAlgebra.Basic"}